_sText:
Map story:
Terrorist group must deliver bomb to Port, they have to drive through an abandoned town called
"Wolfholm". Unknown to them, CT's planted a mine near the entrance of The Town, Terrorist truck is blown up, Terrorist realize that it was an ambush.
Mission
Terrorists:
Eliminate Counter-Terrorists and deliver bomb to the Port
Counter-Terrorists:
Eliminate all terrorists and secure the bomb
